# Auto-load the Nix dev toolchain (Node 22 + CLIs) on `cd` into this directory.
# Requires: nix (flakes enabled) + direnv (+ nix-direnv for caching).
# First-time use: run `direnv allow` once.
use flake

# Keep existing .env (POSTGRES_PASSWORD, API_KEYS, etc.) honored if present.
dotenv_if_exists .env

# Reload the shell when the flake definition changes.
watch_file flake.nix
watch_file flake.lock
